with the clipping.

04:20.165 --> 04:23.252
Forty yards, in the street,
with a silencer.

04:23.337 --> 04:24.131
Very dexterous.

04:24.136 --> 04:25.833
Your father would've
been proud.

04:25.838 --> 04:28.074
Opening up the
international side...

04:28.079 --> 04:29.338
of things like that.

04:29.343 --> 04:31.510
Well, I'll call in again soon.

04:31.594 --> 04:34.763
