at the end, too.

05:02.542 --> 05:05.419
Quite a career.
Quite a legacy.

05:08.965 --> 05:11.674
You're going to be 55, Victor.

05:13.135 --> 05:14.631
I know.

05:14.637 --> 05:17.008
