when you were born.

05:17.014 --> 05:18.093
Indeed.

05:18.098 --> 05:20.011
I've taken up knitting.

05:20.016 --> 05:21.930
Blue for a boy.

05:21.936 --> 05:23.808
We can hope, at least.

05:23.813 --> 05:25.560
Good-bye, mother.

05:25.565 --> 05:28.732
Someone has to carry on
the family business.

05:28.818 --> 05:30.903
These skills mustn't be lost.

05:33.197 --> 05:35.283
