06:32.172 --> 06:34.257
Come in ...

06:35.217 --> 06:37.302
Come in...

06:38.052 --> 06:40.722
- Wrong side of the road!
- Wrong way!

06:40.806 --> 06:42.094
Idiot!

06:42.099 --> 06:45.976
I've got to show, show,
show you...

06:46.062 --> 06:48.812
Come into my bed...

06:48.898 --> 06:53.275
I've got to know,
know, know you...

06:53.359 --> 06:56.245
I have dreams
of orca whales...

06:56.250 --> 06:57.234
and owls...

06:57.239 --> 06:59.824
But I wake up in fear...

06:59.908 --> 07:01.946
You will never be my...

