11:08.238 --> 11:10.323
All right, 9.

11:12.741 --> 11:15.160
900,000, or I'm keeping it.

11:15.245 --> 11:16.407
- What?
- All right, I'll keep it.

11:16.412 --> 11:20.248
Put it back.

11:22.836 --> 11:24.921
One million.

11:26.922 --> 11:29.128
- You're out of your mind.
- All right, I'll keep it.

11:29.133 --> 11:31.218
Stop!

11:32.428 --> 11:34.300
My dear, I'm not a gangster.

11:34.305 --> 11:36.680
But I was in real
estate for 20 years.

11:36.685 --> 11:38.770
I stop at nothing.

11:40.019 --> 11:42.104
Calm down.

11:46.151 --> 11:48.236
I was joking.

11:51.155 --> 11:53.845
- Have that much cash with us?
- Yes, captain.

12:22.560 --> 12:27.523
So now... this jewel...

12:29.234 --> 12:30.802
the ultimate record...

12:30.807 --> 12:33.445
of one man's fearless
conversation...

12:33.529 --> 12:37.031
with his most profound self,
stays with me.

12:38.325 --> 12:39.442
And Mr. Zhirkova...

12:39.447 --> 12:41.407
