13:08.731 --> 13:10.186
It's a fake.

13:10.191 --> 13:12.276
It can't be!

13:12.277 --> 13:14.362
It's a fake!

13:19.743 --> 13:21.281
Oh, yes.

13:21.286 --> 13:23.538
Look at the yellow here,
and you'll--

13:27.125 --> 13:29.210
She switched it.

13:30.295 --> 13:32.380
You don't say.

13:35.717 --> 13:39.302
Trois, deux, un...

13:49.355 --> 13:51.648
