I could get into?

14:00.783 --> 14:02.868
Yep, about this much.

14:09.374 --> 14:11.459
- Rose...
- What?

14:13.588 --> 14:15.210
Don't push your luck too far.

14:15.216 --> 14:17.632
What could happen to me?

14:46.496 --> 14:48.658
He got me with a hook...

14:48.663 --> 14:50.662
Those big bass notes...

14:50.667 --> 14:52.455
Thunder in my chest...

14:52.460 --> 14:55.210
Mm, stuck in my throat...

14:55.294 --> 14:57.379
Pulling me down...

14:57.422 --> 14:58.960
Like a rumble
in the ground...

14:58.965 --> 15:01.342
Crawls up from
the depths...

15:01.427 --> 15:03.512
with a deep down sound...

15:12.730 --> 15:14.393
Watch that man...

15:14.398 --> 15:16.774
See what's in his hands...

15:16.859 --> 15:18.729
Got no joy...

15:18.734 --> 15:20.819
He's a big bad boy

15:32.666 --> 15:34.578
Big bomb body...

15:34.584 --> 15:36.710
Lonely neck...

15:36.796 --> 15:38.708
Swear it was a woman...

15:38.713 --> 15:40.797
That he had in his grip...

15:40.798 --> 15:42.883
Big vibrations, yeah...

15:42.884 --> 15:44.923
