I know.
Just so hopeless...

16:18.087 --> 16:19.874
- See anything you like?
- Sorry?

16:19.879 --> 16:21.794
Oh, um...

16:21.800 --> 16:25.009
- A drink?
- Yeah...

16:25.093 --> 16:26.422
Uh... well...

16:26.428 --> 16:28.132
Bye, sweetheart!

16:28.137 --> 16:30.222
- Bye.
- Oh...

