Johnny got a bam

16:46.947 --> 16:49.033
At last.

16:52.788 --> 16:54.873
Shit.

16:56.499 --> 16:58.585
- All right?
- Mm-hm.

16:59.002 --> 17:00.582
Room 27.

17:00.587 --> 17:02.673
I know.
I remembered.

17:04.132 --> 17:05.627
You've got no messages.

17:05.633 --> 17:08.511
- That's the way I like it.
- Solitary type, huh?

17:10.554 --> 17:12.386
Well, there's a buzzer
by the side of the bed...

17:12.391 --> 17:14.477
if you, uh, change your mind...

17:17.980 --> 17:20.064
What do you weigh?

17:38.041 --> 17:40.126
Yes.

18:15.202 --> 18:17.287
No.

19:48.044 --> 19:50.712
You've committed
the ultimate sin, Victor.

19:50.797 --> 19:53.048
- Mother...
- Oh, don't 'mother' me.

19:53.132 --> 19:55.337
You must win back
your employer's trust.

19:55.342 --> 19:58.761
Your reputation depends on it.
The family reputation.

19:58.845 --> 19:59.967
Yes, mother.

19:59.972 --> 20:02.412
They'll have hired
a competitor by now.

20:03.267 --> 20:05.348
Someone better or
younger than you.

20:05.353 --> 20:07.687
I suppose that's right.

20:07.772 --> 20:09.939
So what do you
think I should do?

20:10.024 --> 20:10.367
Well,

20:10.372 --> 20:13.068
there's only one
thing you can do --...

20:13.152 --> 20:14.599
apologize to the client,

20:14.604 --> 20:16.776
tell him you'll do
the hit for free,

20:16.781 --> 20:18.866
Kill her and return the money.

20:59.657 --> 21:01.612
- Get in the car.
- You killed him!

21:01.618 --> 21:02.904
I had to.
He was going to kill you.

21:02.909 --> 21:04.995
- Oh, okay. Get in the car.
- Keys.

21:08.165 --> 21:10.250
Quickly!

21:13.796 --> 21:15.526
I can't believe they
hired someone...

21:15.531 --> 21:16.043
to kill me.

21:16.048 --> 21:17.961
What am I doing?
What am I doing?

21:17.966 --> 21:20.051
You tell me! Start the car!

21:21.513 --> 21:23.598
Freeze.

21:24.431 --> 21:27.099
Barney? Barney!

21:28.895 --> 21:31.312
Don't tell me.

21:31.398 --> 21:33.483
Out. Now.

21:36.861 --> 21:38.946
Stop!

21:43.951 --> 21:45.697
Face the wall.

21:45.702 --> 21:47.787
Both of you.

22:10.311 --> 22:11.932
Oh, my God.
What have I done?

22:11.937 --> 22:14.022
Who are you?

22:14.523 --> 22:16.608
Who are you?!

22:16.650 --> 22:19.067
You don't know each other?

22:19.152 --> 22:21.442
